direction: right

*.style.border-radius: 8
*.style.font-size: 13
*.style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
*.style.stroke: "#333333"

# --- Entry ---

entry: |md
  **strategy-architecture-review**

  - $ARGUMENTS: RHAISTRAT-NNNN
  - context: fork · model opus
  - invoked by /strategy-review
  - tools: Read, Grep, Glob
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Mode decision ---

mode: |md
  **Mode?**

  - local/strat-tasks present?
  - local vs artifacts (CI)
| {
  shape: diamond
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Cross-reference ---

xref: |md
  **Cross-ref RFE + prior reviews**

  - read strategies (tasks dir)
  - source RFE originals
  - prior reviews (re-review)
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Architecture context gate ---

ctx-check: |md
  **Arch context available?**

  - .context/architecture-context/
    architecture/rhoai-*
| {
  shape: diamond
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Skip branch ---

skip: |md
  **Skip review**

  - "Architecture review skipped
    — no context available"
  - exit cleanly
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Read arch context (external) ---

arch: |md
  **Read arch context**

  - PLATFORM.md
  - component docs per strategy
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#e8e8e8"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
  style.stroke-dash: 3
}

# --- Active overlays (external) ---

overlays: |md
  **Active overlays**

  - overlays/*.md (status: active)
  - human-authored corrections
  - take precedence over docs
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#e8e8e8"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
  style.stroke-dash: 3
}

# --- Assess (LLM) ---

assess: |md
  **Assess architecture**

  - dependencies correct?
  - integration patterns valid?
  - component boundaries respected?
  - deployment model correct?
  - platform conflicts?
  - cross-component coordination?
  - cite arch docs for every finding
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#e8e8e8"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
  style.double-border: true
}

# --- Verdict output ---

output-verdict: |md
  **Structured verdict**

  - Architecture assessment
  - Missing dependencies
  - Incorrect assumptions
  - Cross-component risks
  - Recommendation
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Flow ---

entry -> mode
mode -> xref: "local"
mode -> xref: "CI"
xref -> ctx-check
ctx-check -> skip: "none"
ctx-check -> arch: "available"
arch -> overlays
overlays -> assess
assess -> output-verdict
